flocksimulator.domain

Class Generator

  • java.lang.Object
    • flocksimulator.domain.Generator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AgentGenerator, SpatialAgentGenerator

    public abstract class Generator
extends Object
    Class for defining agents desired behaviors and parameters for those behaviors, as well as, creating agents and keeping track of them. The way of querying agents is specified by the implementations of this class
    Author:
    peje
